{"metadata":{"role":"sampleCode","title":"Accelerate your app with CarPlay","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC20"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"CarPlay is the smarter, safer way for people to use iPhone in the car. We’ll show you how to build great apps for the car screen, and introduce you to developing CarPlay apps in categories like EV charging, parking, and quick food ordering. We’ll also share how existing audio and communication apps can take advantage of improvements to the CarPlay framework to create a more flexible UI."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-10635-Accelerate-your-app-with-CarPlay"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"overridingTitle":"Watch Video (26 min)","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2020\/10635","type":"reference","isActive":true},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc20-10635-accelerate-your-app-with-carplay"]}],"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Related Sessions","anchor":"Related-Sessions","type":"heading","level":2},{"style":"list","items":["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC22-10016-Get-more-mileage-out-of-your-app-with-CarPlay","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC19-207-Introducing-SiriKit-Media-Intents","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC18-213-CarPlay-Audio-and-Navigation-Apps"],"type":"links"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"WWDC20.jpeg":{"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC20.jpeg","alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC20":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode 12, Swift 5.3, iOS 14, macOS 11 (Big Sur), tvOS 14, watchOS 7."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"New APIs: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"WidgetKit"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"StoreKit Testing"},{"type":"text","text":", and more."}],"role":"collectionGroup","type":"topic","title":"WWDC20","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20","images":[{"identifier":"WWDC20-Icon.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"WWDC20.jpeg","type":"card"}],"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc20"},"WWDC20-Icon.png":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-Icon.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC20-Icon.png","alt":null},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC18-213-CarPlay-Audio-and-Navigation-Apps":{"kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"Learn how to update your audio or navigation app to support CarPlay. Apps in CarPlay are optimized for use in the car, and automatically adapt to available vehicle screens and input controls. Audio apps can deliver music, news, podcasts, and more. With the new CarPlay framework, Navigation apps can provide detailed maps, destination search, turn-by-turn guidance, and user notifications.","type":"text"}],"role":"sampleCode","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC18-213-CarPlay-Audio-and-Navigation-Apps","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc18-213-carplay-audio-and-navigation-apps","title":"CarPlay Audio and Navigation Apps"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC22-10016-Get-more-mileage-out-of-your-app-with-CarPlay":{"title":"Get more mileage out of your app with CarPlay","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc22-10016-get-more-mileage-out-of-your-app-with-carplay","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"CarPlay is a smarter, safer way to use your iPhone while you drive. Learn about the latest app types for CarPlay and discover how the CarPlay Simulator can help you develop and test apps without leaving your desk. We’ll also explore how navigation apps can connect with digital instrument clusters in supported vehicles."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC22-10016-Get-more-mileage-out-of-your-app-with-CarPlay","kind":"article","role":"sampleCode"},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"url":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn More…"}],"type":"link","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","title":"Learn More…"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC19-207-Introducing-SiriKit-Media-Intents":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"iOS 13 enhances SiriKit by bringing all new support for audio content playback. See how to provide an excellent, hands-free experience for playing your music, audiobooks, podcasts, radio, and more. Dive into best practices for handling search terms, discover how to provide a complete experience with playback speeds, adding to playlists, and allowing customers to tell you if they like or dislike content."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC19-207-Introducing-SiriKit-Media-Intents","type":"topic","role":"sampleCode","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc19-207-introducing-sirikit-media-intents","kind":"article","title":"Introducing SiriKit Media Intents"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDCNotes.png"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"WWDC Notes","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Session notes shared by the community for the community."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes"},"WWDCNotes.png":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","alt":null},"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2020/10635":{"type":"download","checksum":null,"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2020\/10635","url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2020\/10635"}}}